	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'd like to get into NES or SNES development, but which one is easier to start with?
<br />
<br />It seems likes theres a lack of docs for the SNES, as I couldn't find much out there, as compared to the NES.
<br />
<br />I'm fairly familiar with 6502 machine language, as I used to write apps for the C64 (not games). Having kernel routines to do the basics makes things easier.

		

		</td>
